<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SAE India · BIT Sindri</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#15171c;
  --bg-soft:#1c1f26;
  --bg-soft-2:#21252d;
  --bg-card:#1a1d24;
  --line:rgba(244,241,230,0.09);
  --line-strong:rgba(244,241,230,0.18);
  --red:#c8203a;
  --red-deep:#8e1626;
  --green:#1f6f4a;
  --green-deep:#154f35;
  --gold:#f2a93b;
  --gold-deep:#c9821f;
  --ink:#f4f1e6;
  --ink-muted:#a3aab2;
  --ink-dim:#6e7580;
  --radius:14px;
  --radius-sm:8px;
  --maxw:1180px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{
  margin:0;
  background:var(--bg);
  color:var(--ink);
  font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  line-height:1.5;
  position:relative;
}
h1,h2,h3,h4{
  font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  letter-spacing:0.01em;
  margin:0;
  font-weight:600;
}
p{margin:0;}
a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none;}
ul{margin:0;padding:0;list-style:none;}
button{font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer;}
.mono{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;}
::selection{background:var(--gold);color:#15171c;}
:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--gold);outline-offset:3px;border-radius:4px;}

/* ---------- background atmosphere layer ---------- */
.bg-layer{
  position:fixed;
  inset:0;
  z-index:0;
  overflow:hidden;
  pointer-events:none;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 18% 12%, rgba(31,111,74,0.16), transparent 42%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 86% 78%, rgba(200,32,58,0.14), transparent 45%),
    var(--bg);
}
.bg-grid{
  position:absolute;
  inset:0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(var(--line) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, var(--line) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size:46px 46px;
  opacity:0.55;
}
.bg-art{
  position:absolute;
  opacity:0.5;
}
.bg-art.drone{
  top:-40px;
  right:-60px;
  width:46vw;
  max-width:560px;
  min-width:300px;
  transform:rotate(8deg);
}
.buggy-photo-bg{
  background-image:url('data:image/jpeg;base64,');
  background-repeat:no-repeat;
  background-position:center;
  background-size:contain;
}
.bg-art.buggy{
  top:50%;
  left:50%;
  transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
  width:70vw;
  height:auto;
  aspect-ratio:720/870;
  max-width:700px;
  min-width:300px;
  mix-blend-mode:screen;
  background-size:contain;
  background-position:center;
  background-repeat:no-repeat;
}
.bg-scrim{
  position:absolute;
  inset:0;
  background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(21,23,28,0.35) 0%, rgba(21,23,28,0.60) 40%, rgba(21,23,28,0.80) 100%);
}

/* ---------- header ---------- */
.site-header{
  position:sticky;
  top:0;
  z-index:50;
  background:rgba(21,23,28,0.86);
  backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
}
.header-top{
  max-width:var(--maxw);
  margin:0 auto;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;
  gap:18px;
  padding:14px 22px;
}
.crest{
  height:54px;
  width:54px;
  flex:none;
  border-radius:50%;
  object-fit:cover;
  background:#0e0f12;
  box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--line-strong), 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
}
.crest.right{height:58px;width:58px;}
.brandblock{
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  align-items:center;
  text-align:center;
  flex:1;
  min-width:0;
}
.brand-eyebrow{
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;
  font-size:10.5px;
  letter-spacing:0.22em;
  color:var(--gold);
  text-transform:uppercase;
}
.brand-name{
  font-size:clamp(18px,3.4vw,26px);
  letter-spacing:0.04em;
  line-height:1.05;
  margin-top:2px;
}
.brand-name span{color:var(--red);}
.header-nav-row{
  border-top:1px solid var(--line);
}
.nav-wrap{
  max-width:var(--maxw);
  margin:0 auto;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  padding:0 22px;
}
.site-nav{
  display:flex;
  gap:4px;
  padding:8px 0;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  justify-content:center;
}
.nav-link{
  font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;
  font-size:13px;
  letter-spacing:0.06em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  padding:8px 16px;
  border-radius:999px;
  color:var(--ink-muted);
  border:1px solid transparent;
  transition:all .18s ease;
}
.nav-link:hover{color:var(--ink);border-color:var(--line-strong);}
.nav-link.active{
  color:var(--bg);
  background:var(--gold);
  border-color:var(--gold);
}

/* ---------- layout shell ---------- */
main{position:relative;z-index:1;}
.page{display:none;max-width:var(--maxw);margin:0 auto;padding:48px 22px 90px;}
.page.active{display:block;animation:fadein .35s ease;}
@keyframes fadein{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}

.page-head{margin-bottom:38px;max-width:680px;}
.page-head .eyebrow{
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;
  font-size:12px;
  letter-spacing:0.18em;
  color:var(--gold);
  text-transform:uppercase;
}
.page-head h1{font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,46px);margin-top:8px;}
.page-head .sub{color:var(--ink-muted);margin-top:10px;font-size:15.5px;}

/* ---------- buttons ---------- */
.btn{
  display:inline-flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:8px;
  padding:12px 22px;
  border-radius:999px;
  font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;
  font-size:13.5px;
  letter-spacing:0.05em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  border:1px solid var(--line-strong);
  transition:all .18s ease;
}
.btn-primary{background:var(--red);border-color:var(--red);color:#fff;}
.btn-primary:hover{background:#e02745;}
.btn-ghost{color:var(--ink);}
.btn-ghost:hover{background:var(--bg-soft);border-color:var(--ink-dim);}

/* ---------- dashboard hero ---------- */
.hero{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr;
  gap:36px;
  align-items:center;
  padding-bottom:46px;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
}
.hero-copy .eyebrow{
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;
  font-size:12px;
  letter-spacing:0.2em;
  color:var(--gold);
}
.hero-copy h1{
  font-size:clamp(34px,5.6vw,54px);
  line-height:1.04;
  margin-top:12px;
}
.hero-copy h1 em{color:var(--red);font-style:normal;}
.hero-copy p{color:var(--ink-muted);margin-top:16px;font-size:16px;max-width:480px;}
.hero-ctas{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-top:26px;flex-wrap:wrap;}

.hero-panel{
  position:relative;
  min-height:300px;
  border:1px solid var(--line-strong);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(242,169,59,0.10), transparent 60%),
    var(--bg-soft);
  overflow:hidden;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  padding:18px;
}
.hero-photo{
  width:100%;
  height:100%;
  min-height:280px;
  filter:drop-shadow(0 18px 26px rgba(0,0,0,0.45));
}
.callout{
  position:absolute;
  background:rgba(21,23,28,0.86);
  border:1px solid var(--line-strong);
  border-radius:8px;
  padding:7px 11px;
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;
  font-size:11px;
  color:var(--ink);
  backdrop-filter:blur(4px);
  white-space:nowrap;
}
.callout b{color:var(--gold);display:block;font-size:13px;}
.callout.c1{top:10%;left:6%;}
.callout.c2{top:8%;right:6%;}
.callout.c3{bottom:10%;left:8%;}
.callout.c4{bottom:14%;right:5%;}

/* ---------- stat strip ---------- */
.stat-strip{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
  gap:1px;
  background:var(--line);
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  overflow:hidden;
  margin:42px 0;
}
.stat{
  background:var(--bg-soft);
  padding:22px 18px;
  text-align:center;
}
.stat .num{
  font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;
  font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,30px);
  color:var(--gold);
}
.stat .lbl{
  font-size:11.5px;
  color:var(--ink-muted);
  text-transform:uppercase;
  letter-spacing:0.05em;
  margin-top:6px;
}

/* ---------- section heading shared ---------- */
.block-head{
  display:flex;
  align-items:baseline;
  justify-content:space-between;
  gap:12px;
  margin:48px 0 20px;
}
.block-head h2{font-size:22px;color:var(--ink);}
.block-head .tag{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-dim);letter-spacing:0.12em;}

/* ---------- news cards ---------- */
.news-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;}
.news-card{
  background:var(--bg-card);
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
  padding:18px;
}
.news-card .date{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--green);text-transform:uppercase;}
.news-card h3{font-size:16px;margin-top:8px;text-transform:none;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:700;}
.news-card p{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-top:8px;}

/* ---------- quick nav cards ---------- */
.quick-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:14px;}
.quick-card{
  background:var(--bg-card);
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
  padding:20px 18px;
  transition:all .18s ease;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap:10px;
}
.quick-card:hover{border-color:var(--gold);transform:translateY(-3px);}
.quick-card .ic{color:var(--gold);}
.quick-card h3{font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.03em;}
.quick-card p{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-muted);}

/* ---------- events timeline ---------- */
.filters{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:30px;}
.chip{
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;
  font-size:11.5px;
  letter-spacing:0.05em;
  padding:7px 14px;
  border-radius:999px;
  border:1px solid var(--line-strong);
  color:var(--ink-muted);
  text-transform:uppercase;
  background:transparent;
}
.chip.active{background:var(--green);border-color:var(--green);color:#fff;}
.timeline{position:relative;padding-left:28px;border-left:1px dashed var(--line-strong);}
.tl-item{position:relative;padding-bottom:30px;}
.tl-item::before{
  content:'';
  position:absolute;
  left:-34px;
  top:4px;
  width:11px;height:11px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--gold);
  box-shadow:0 0 0 4px var(--bg);
}
.tl-card{
  background:var(--bg-card);
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
  padding:18px 20px;
}
.tl-top{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px;}
.tl-tag{
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;
  font-size:10.5px;
  letter-spacing:0.08em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  padding:3px 9px;
  border-radius:5px;
  color:#fff;
}
.tl-tag.workshop{background:var(--green);}
.tl-tag.visit{background:var(--gold-deep);}
.tl-tag.flagship{background:var(--red);}
.tl-tag.recruit{background:#3a6ea8;}
.tl-term{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-dim);}
.tl-card h3{font-size:17px;text-transform:none;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:700;}
.tl-card p{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-top:6px;}
.tl-loc{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-dim);margin-top:8px;display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;}

/* ---------- competitions ---------- */
.comp-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:18px;}
.comp-card{
  background:var(--bg-card);
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:22px;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap:10px;
}
.comp-card .ic{
  width:42px;height:42px;
  border-radius:10px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  background:var(--bg-soft-2);
  color:var(--gold);
}
.comp-card h3{font-size:18px;}
.comp-card .team-of{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--green);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;}
.comp-card p{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-muted);}
.badge{
  margin-top:auto;
  border:1px dashed var(--line-strong);
  border-radius:7px;
  padding:8px 10px;
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;
  font-size:11px;
  color:var(--ink-dim);
  text-align:center;
}
.hof{
  margin-top:36px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(242,169,59,0.10), rgba(200,32,58,0.06));
  border:1px solid var(--line-strong);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:24px 26px;
}
.hof h3{font-size:15px;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:0.05em;}
.hof p{font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-top:8px;max-width:760px;}

/* ---------- bearers / team ---------- */
.advisor-card{
  display:flex;
  gap:20px;
  align-items:center;
  background:var(--bg-card);
  border:1px solid var(--line-strong);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:22px 26px;
  margin-bottom:34px;
}
.avatar{
  flex:none;
  width:64px;height:64px;
  border-radius:50%;
  border:1.5px dashed var(--line-strong);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;
  font-size:18px;
  color:var(--ink-dim);
  background:var(--bg-soft-2);
}
.advisor-card .avatar{width:76px;height:76px;font-size:22px;border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold);}
.advisor-info .role-tag{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;}
.advisor-info h3{font-size:19px;margin-top:4px;text-transform:none;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-dim);}
.advisor-info p{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-dim);margin-top:4px;}

.bearer-grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(208px, 1fr));
  gap:14px;
}
.member-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:14px;}
.bearer-card,.member-card{
  background:var(--bg-card);
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
  padding:18px 14px;
  text-align:center;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:8px;
}
.bearer-card{justify-content:flex-start;}
.bearer-card .role-tag{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:1.4;min-height:28px;display:flex;align-items:center;}
.bearer-card .nm,.member-card .nm{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-dim);font-weight:600;}
.avatar-row{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;}
.avatar-unit{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
.avatar-unit .avatar{width:54px;height:54px;font-size:14px;}
.social-row{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:4px;}
.social-row a{
  width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  border:1px solid var(--line-strong);color:var(--ink-dim);
}
.member-card .role-tag{font-size:9.5px;color:var(--ink-dim);}

.team-section{margin-bottom:46px;}
.team-section-head{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:14px;margin-bottom:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.team-section-head h2{font-size:21px;}
.team-section-head .team-blurb{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-muted);}
.team-divider{height:1px;background:var(--line);margin:14px 0 22px;}

/* ---------- footer ---------- */
footer{
  position:relative;z-index:1;
  border-top:1px solid var(--line);
  background:rgba(15,17,21,0.7);
  padding:40px 22px 28px;
}
.footer-wrap{max-width:var(--maxw);margin:0 auto;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:30px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.footer-brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
.footer-brand img{height:38px;width:38px;border-radius:50%;}
.footer-brand .nm{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.03em;}
.footer-brand .nm span{color:var(--red);}
.footer-meta{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-dim);margin-top:6px;}
.footer-links{display:flex;gap:10px;}
.footer-links a{
  width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;
  border:1px solid var(--line-strong);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  color:var(--ink-muted);
  transition:all .18s ease;
}
.footer-links a:hover{color:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold);}
.footer-bottom{
  max-width:var(--maxw);margin:24px auto 0;
  border-top:1px solid var(--line);
  padding-top:18px;
  font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-dim);
  display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;
}

/* ---------- mobile nav toggle ---------- */
.nav-toggle{display:none;}

/* ---------- responsive ---------- */
@media (max-width:920px){
  .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .hero-panel{min-height:240px;order:-1;}
  .news-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
  .quick-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
  .comp-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
  .member-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);}
  .stat-strip{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
}
@media (max-width:680px){
  .header-top{padding:12px 16px;gap:10px;}
  .crest{height:42px;width:42px;}
  .crest.right{height:46px;width:46px;}
  .brand-eyebrow{font-size:8.5px;letter-spacing:0.14em;}
  .brand-name{font-size:15px;}
  .site-nav{gap:2px;}
  .nav-link{padding:7px 11px;font-size:11px;}
  .news-grid,.quick-grid,.comp-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .member-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
  .advisor-card{flex-direction:column;text-align:center;}
  .footer-wrap{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;}
  .callout{font-size:9.5px;padding:5px 8px;}
  .callout b{font-size:11px;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="bg-layer" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="bg-grid"></div>

  <div class="bg-art buggy buggy-photo-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>


  <div class="bg-scrim"></div>
</div>

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-top">
    <img class="crest left" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="BIT Sindri Institute Crest">
    <div class="brandblock">
      <span class="brand-eyebrow">Society of Automotive Engineers · Collegiate Club</span>
      <h1 class="brand-name">SAE INDIA <span>BIT SINDRI</span></h1>
    </div>
    <img class="crest right" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="SAE India BIT Sindri Logo">
  </div>
  <div class="header-nav-row">
    <div class="nav-wrap">
      <nav class="site-nav" id="siteNav">
        <a href="#dashboard" class="nav-link" data-page="dashboard">Dashboard</a>
        <a href="#events" class="nav-link" data-page="events">Events</a>
        <a href="#competitions" class="nav-link" data-page="competitions">Competitions</a>
        <a href="#bearers" class="nav-link" data-page="bearers">Office Bearers</a>
        <a href="#team" class="nav-link" data-page="team">Team</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main>

  <!-- ===================== DASHBOARD ===================== -->
  <section class="page" id="page-dashboard">
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <span class="eyebrow mono">EST. MARCH 2010 — BIT SINDRI, JHARKHAND</span>
        <h1>Engineering the <em>next lap.</em></h1>
        <p>We design, build and race vehicles from the ground up — chasing podiums at BAJA, SUPRA and EFFICYCLE, and pushing into the skies with Vayu, our aero &amp; UAV wing.</p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a href="#competitions" class="btn btn-primary" data-page="competitions">Explore Competitions</a>
          <a href="#team" class="btn btn-ghost" data-page="team">Meet the Team</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-panel">
        <div class="hero-photo buggy-photo-bg" role="img" aria-label="SAE India BIT Sindri BAJA vehicle"></div>
        <div class="callout c1"><b>Est. 2010</b>Chapter founded</div>
        <div class="callout c2"><b>4</b>Active sub-teams</div>
        <div class="callout c3"><b>BAJA · SUPRA</b>EFFICYCLE entries</div>
        <div class="callout c4"><b>Vayu</b>Aero &amp; UAV wing</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stat-strip">
      <div class="stat"><div class="num mono">2010</div><div class="lbl">Chapter Founded</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num mono">03</div><div class="lbl">Flagship SAE Events</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num mono">04</div><div class="lbl">Sub-Teams</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num mono">1949</div><div class="lbl">BIT Sindri Founded</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="block-head">
      <h2>Latest Transmission</h2>
      <span class="tag">// chapter updates</span>
    </div>
    <div class="news-grid" id="newsGrid"></div>

    <div class="block-head">
      <h2>Find Your Way In</h2>
      <span class="tag">// quick links</span>
    </div>
    <div class="quick-grid">
      <a class="quick-card" href="#events" data-page="events">
        <span class="ic">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M8 3v4M16 3v4"/></svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Events</h3>
        <p>Workshops, drives &amp; the build calendar.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="quick-card" href="#competitions" data-page="competitions">
        <span class="ic">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M3 12h4l2-7 4 14 2-7h6"/></svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Competitions</h3>
        <p>BAJA, SUPRA, EFFICYCLE &amp; Aerothon.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="quick-card" href="#bearers" data-page="bearers">
        <span class="ic">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 12a4 4 0 100-8 4 4 0 000 8zM4 21c0-4 4-6 8-6s8 2 8 6"/></svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Office Bearers</h3>
        <p>The crew steering the chapter.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="quick-card" href="#team" data-page="team">
        <span class="ic">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="8" cy="9" r="3"/><circle cx="17" cy="10" r="2.4"/><path d="M2 20c0-3 2.7-5 6-5s6 2 6 5M14.5 20c.3-2.2 2-4 4.5-4.2"/></svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Team</h3>
        <p>Four crews, one chapter.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== EVENTS ===================== -->
  <section class="page" id="page-events">
    <div class="page-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">// chapter calendar</span>
      <h1>Events</h1>
      <p class="sub">Workshops, drives, inductions and the flagship moments that build a team — fill in exact dates as your term calendar is locked.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="filters" id="eventFilters"></div>
    <div class="timeline" id="eventTimeline"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== COMPETITIONS ===================== -->
  <section class="page" id="page-competitions">
    <div class="page-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">// what we build for</span>
      <h1>Competitions</h1>
      <p class="sub">Where blueprints meet the track — and, with Vayu, the sky. Each crew owns its build end-to-end: design, fabrication, testing and race day.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="comp-grid" id="compGrid"></div>
    <div class="hof">
      <h3 class="mono">// HALL OF FAME</h3>
      <p>Over the chapter's history, teams have placed in inter-collegiate technical challenges beyond SAE's own events — including a first-place design win for a student-built submarine at IIT Kharagpur and a podium finish at a cliff-rescue challenge at IIT(ISM) Dhanbad. Add your latest results here as they come in.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== OFFICE BEARERS ===================== -->
  <section class="page" id="page-bearers">
    <div class="page-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">// term leadership</span>
      <h1>Office Bearers</h1>
      <p class="sub">The crew steering the chapter this term. Add a photo for each member to fill the circles below.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="advisor-card">
      <div class="avatar">FA</div>
      <div class="advisor-info">
        <span class="role-tag">Faculty Advisor</span>
        <h3>Dr Manoj Kumar</h3>
        <p>Department of Mechanical Engineering, BIT Sindri</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bearer-grid" id="bearerGrid"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== TEAM ===================== -->
  <section class="page" id="page-team">
    <div class="page-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">// four crews, one chapter</span>
      <h1>The Team</h1>
      <p class="sub">Every member listed below is a placeholder slot — drop in real names, roles and photos for the current build season.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="teamSections"></div>
  </section>

</main>

